 < Theorem append_values_total :
     forall LA LB, is_list is_value LA -> exists L, LA ++ LB = L.

============================
 forall LA LB, is_list is_value LA -> exists L, LA ++ LB = L

 < induction on 1.

IH : forall LA LB, is_list is_value LA * -> exists L, LA ++ LB = L
============================
 forall LA LB, is_list is_value LA @ -> exists L, LA ++ LB = L

 < intros Is.

Variables: LA LB
IH : forall LA LB, is_list is_value LA * -> exists L, LA ++ LB = L
Is : is_list is_value LA @
============================
 exists L, LA ++ LB = L

 < Is: case Is.

Subgoal 1:

Variables: LB
IH : forall LA LB, is_list is_value LA * -> exists L, LA ++ LB = L
============================
 exists L, [] ++ LB = L

 < search.
